job_details.full_text:
Full Stack Developer for UX-centric App

I am seeking a seasoned full-stack software developer to assist in the creation of a dual Web and Mobile application. This application will primarily focus on user authentication and profiles, employing a two-factor authentication system for enhanced security., Develop a mobile-first, user-friendly interface

profile_classification.rationale: The job description focuses on full-stack development for a user-centric application, specifically mentioning user authentication and profiles with two-factor authentication. It does not mention any specific AI technologies, models, or methodologies, nor does it involve tasks related to machine learning model development, training, or deployment. The role appears to be a traditional software engineering position, not directly related to AI or Generative AI.

job_tasks.justification: The description explicitly states 'seasoned full-stack software developer' and mentions developing a 'dual Web and Mobile application', 'user-friendly interface', and 'user authentication'. These are core software development activities.
Focuses on building the user interface for the application, a key aspect of software development.
Describes a specific feature of the application that requires software implementation.
